description: The 101 NFT Pepe Project is a unique and innovative art initiative that combines the popular internet meme "Pepe the Frog" with the revolutionary technology of Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) and the Bitcoin blockchain. This project features a collection of 101 limited edition Pepe illustrations.By linking the NFTs to the Bitcoin blockchain, the 101 NFT Pepe Project ensures the authenticity, provenance, and scarcity of each artwork, creating a digital art collection that is secure, verifiable, and easily tradable among collectors and enthusiasts. This groundbreaking fusion of art, blockchain technology, and Bitcoin's microtransactions brings a new dimension to the NFT space and adds value to the ever-growing world of digital collectibles. No promises and utility just on special satribute
name: Redacted Frog
